* TIM2 -- shared reminder display for TIMR (REXX) and TIMC (COBOL).
* Rendered by the scheduled transaction after its EXEC CICS RETRIEVE
* picks up the FROM(...) payload from the originating START. ENTER
* dismisses the reminder and returns the terminal to the blank prompt.
MAP TIM2 SIZE 24x80
  FIELD AT 0,2  LEN 30 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=BLUE  "Timed Reminder -- fired"
  FIELD AT 0,60 LEN 5  PROT COLOR=BLUE         "TERM="
  INPUT TERMID  AT 0,65 LEN 8  PROT COLOR=BLUE
  FIELD AT 4,4  LEN 60 PROT COLOR=BLUE         "Your scheduled reminder is up:"
  INPUT MSG     AT 8,4  LEN 70 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=YELLOW
  INPUT FIRED   AT 12,4 LEN 30 PROT COLOR=TURQUOISE
  FIELD AT 22,2 LEN 50 PROT COLOR=BLUE         "ENTER=Dismiss"
  CURSOR        AT 22,2
ENDMAP
